reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely love these!
reviews.reviewText: These throw pillows have been wonderful! The material seems much more thicker and somewhat durable than most covers I have ordered before. While I say they are more durable one did rip at the zipper seam when I was trying to shove a pillow in it, BUT in the covers defense the pillow was super stuffed and exactly 18x18 so it was probably a little too much for the cover to handle. However once it was filled it zipped right up and has looked amazing in our living room. The colors are fantastic although it does have somewhat of a coral/orange stitching on it, which wasn't an issue to me I love a little pop of color here and there, but someone else may not like it so it was something to note. I would definitely recommend these, they are so trendy, and break up the monotony of a solid color pillow and seem to be quality made and durable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love these covers! Neutral colors and a simple design. Well made and an easy way to transform your old boring couch. I paired them with some solid color pillows and they look great! They are exactly as described and delivered on time as promised.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I just love these boho throw pillow covers! The tufted chenille and linen fabric is such high quality and they are sewn beautifully. The pattern and tufting is on the front of the pillows and the plain linen fabric is on the back. The colors look absolutely true to what I see in the product photos. They shipped folded nicely in heavier zip bag - there is virtually no fold or crease marks in this heavier weight fabric. I stuffed one of my covers with a 21 x21 insert and while it did require some pushing and squishing and slowly maneuvering the zipper- the end result looks fantastic! They were absolutely no smells of any kind coming from these covers upon opening them. Do yourself a favor and get these pillow covers!

reviews.reviewText: These throw pillows bring color and texture to my neutral living room. I have a combination of gray and beige with rust accents and these pillows tie all the colors together. Very well made and sturdy.
